data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. RESORT STYLE LIVING at its finest! This waterfront oasis is perfect for an investor looking for a SHORT TERM RENTAL property (offered furnished), primary or vacation home.  SO MANY UPDATES in the last 3 years….Solar panels, roof, impact windows, hvac, hybrid water heater and appliances. This home comes complete with a boat lift, dock (110/220v electric and water), jet ski dock and an additional boat slip so you can make a quick escape to the Gulf of Mexico. Enter through the courtyard into your 3 bed/2.5 bath split floorplan home.  Your eye is immediately drawn to the wrap around windows with expansive water views, and you are greeted by soaring ceilings and a wide-open floor plan.  The kitchen features maple cabinetry, newer appliances, and quartz countertops. The generously sized master bedroom has a double-sided wood burning fireplace and is a true retreat with impressive water views.  What a view to wake up to!  In addition to the 3 bedrooms, you will find a study with French doors…perfect for a home office, playroom or extra space for guests!  Head outside to your BACKYARD PARADISE!  The heated beach entry pool is a show stopper with a Pebble Tech finish and an amazing grotto with a waterfall. Catch some rays on the pavered pool deck or relax in the shade of the extended covered patio.  There is also a large additional storage closet for all your beach toys!  On the west side of the home there is plenty of room for RV parking or additional boat storage. This is a sought-after location, just a short walk to the beautiful white sands of the GULF OF MEXICO! Enjoy all that this quaint beach community has to offer; fantastic dining, shopping, music festivals, arts and craft fairs, parks, nature walk, tennis courts/pickleball and more!.
